.page-header
  %h1 Everyone

.page-header
  %h2
    %small POST
    \/users

%p Create an user.

%h3 Parameters
%table.bordered-table
  %tbody
    %tr
      %td user[name]
      %td John Doe
    %tr
      %td user[email]
      %td john@doe.org
    %tr
      %td user[password]
      %td something

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users

.page-header
  %h2
    %small GET
    \/users/verify

%p
  Sign in with an user. It will return a user object with token.
  Just send it on every request as parameter named
  %code auth_token
  \.

%h3 Parameters
%table.bordered-table
  %tbody
    %tr
      %td email
      %td john@doe.org
    %tr
      %td password
      %td something

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/verify

.page-header
  %h2
    %small GET
    \/users/facebookconnect

%p Use Facebook connect. It return an user object with an access token if the connection was successful.

%h3 Parameters
%table.bordered-table
  %tbody
    %tr
      %td facebookToken
      %td XYZXYZXYZXYZXYZ

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/facebookconnect

.page-header
  %h2
    %small GET|PUT
    \/users/self

%p
  Returns current user. Or update it by using PUT method.

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/self

.page-header
  %h1 Protected

.page-header
  %h2
    %small GET
    \/users/search

%p Search for users.

%h3 Parameters
%table.bordered-table
  %tbody
    %tr
      %td name
      %td Benjamin

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/search?name=benjamin

.page-header
  %h2
    %small DELETE
    \/users/id

%p Destroy an user from database.

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/{id}

.page-header
  %h2
    %small PUT
    \/users/id/addadmin

%p Grant admin access to an user.

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/{id}/addadmin

.page-header
  %h2
    %small PUT
    \/users/id/removeadmin

%p Revoke admin access to an user.

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/{id}/removeadmin

.page-header
  %h2
    %small GET
    \/users/admins

%p Get list of all admins.

%p
  %span.label EXAMPLE

%pre
  http://voxe.org/api/v1/users/admins
